Package kowalski.tools.data.xml

This package contains classes auto-generated from the XML schema describing the structure of the Kowalski XML project data, Do not edit the java code in this package! Instead, edit the XML schema kowalski.xsd and run the compile-xsd ant task to generate new java code.
